originalText.text: Nick is incredible. Not only does he know the area incredibly well, he’s also very invested in his clients. He immediately understood what we wanted, always responded quickly, and gave us daily updates on properties in the area. For a process that I expected to take many weeks, we were able to find a great apartment complex within a day or two through Nick and land on our dream apartment in under a week. Couldn’t recommend Nick more.

originalText.text: I worked with Nick! He’s the most helpful person I’ve come across. Despite me not initially being physically present in NYC, he created custom listings for me and communicated with people on my behalf. When I was in NYC, he helped me at every step of getting an apartment — bringing me a sense of comfort that I had someone trustworthy looking after. Especially for someone like me who was renting in NYC for the first time. He’s quick with communication, super helpful and always tries to solve your problem. I couldn’t recommend him more!

originalText.text: Nick was amazingly helpful and in the know about where to rent in New York. He was able to point us in the right direction from the beginning, saving us a lot of time. When the building started making things tricky, Nick intervened and landed us the apartment immediately after a phone call to the building. Strongly recommend Nick for his professionalism and knowledge.
